I"ê<p>Are you looking for a way to add riddles to your application? Rather than build the feature yourself, you can use this pre-built API. The Riddles API can return riddles from a variety of categories. Current categories include easy, hard, kids, math, word, and funny. Request one random riddle or request them all! Riddles in the original database are from <a href="https://parade.com/947956/parade/riddles/">https://parade.com/947956/parade/riddles/</a>. New riddles can be added and updated via the API.</p>

<p class="success">Authentication</p>

<p>No authentication is needed to use this API.</p>

